<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>槽边往事 | wechat-feeds</title><link>http://MjM5MjAzODU2MA.favicon.privacyhide.com/favicon.ico</link><description> </description><managingEditor> (hellodword)</managingEditor><pubDate>Thu, 11 Mar 2021 13:29:20 +0800</pubDate><image><url>http://MjM5MjAzODU2MA.favicon.privacyhide.com/favicon.ico</url><title>槽边往事 | wechat-feeds</title><link>http://MjM5MjAzODU2MA.favicon.privacyhide.com/favicon.ico</link><width>64</width><height>64</height></image><item><title>还在写就不错了</title><link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/289Os2v59oFfD1wuxKntdg</link><description></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ia6gU9JNtkqBEMw9Rib9iabZtFACv3pjpUQaXgqn5QyLJsXuZlE6DltUMUruN37MOrpLiaApZNst0FTfavKlHEd0w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br>还在写就不错了，这是我最近经常用来劝人的一句话。每次有朋友或者网友抱怨如今的纯文学作品，我就会这么回答。]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Thu, 11 Mar 2021 12:07:19 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>余华新作《文城》读后</title><link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/aH2v41SjhKwbElWSljY-HQ</link><description></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ia6gU9JNtkoI0kLRAUAI368rXYTUaibw581pCpvicQR5fzbibD6vZ1PhZGJW4icOqdWgN4icTFicbtqZVgCibJsEdhvRg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br>连着两天咔咔整了两本严肃文学，哎妈，给我整的，瞅谁都苦大仇深，精神层次噌噌地往上那叫一个提溜得快啊。]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 10 Mar 2021 09:11:12 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>《克拉拉与太阳》读后</title><link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/KeNuMCBwywDF6tXQlkLxBQ</link><description></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Ia6gU9JNtkoI0kLRAUAI368rXYTUaibw56YBgZmXfDueW1e45MiadezsGgsPna7G9TpDIZJJ4AIoHdaPD1gTjWYw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br>石黑一雄新著《克拉拉与太阳》读完了，写一篇读后感记录一下自己的想法。]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 09 Mar 2021 09:57:53 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>祝各位女读者节日快乐</title><link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/vNz3iK2JfUihlnSE7